Class LoginEmployerViewStub

java.lang.Object
com.example.networkmeup.view.LoginTest.LoginEmployerTest.LoginEmployerViewStub
All Implemented Interfaces:
LoginEmployerView
public class LoginEmployerViewStub extends Object implements LoginEmployerView
This class represents a stub of the Employer Login View used for testing purposes. It implements the LoginEmployerView interface to simulate user interface actions and display feedback.
